1.Declare Page Function Variable

var scrollPos;

2.Add to DA Javascript Expression

FOR MODAL DIALOG

*Before Refresh  
scrollPos = $('.t-Dialog-bodyWrapperIn').scrollTop();
*After Refresh
$('.t-Dialog-bodyWrapperIn').scrollTop(scrollPos); 

FOR NORMAL PAGE

*Before Refresh  
scrollPos = $(window).scrollTop();
*After Refresh
$(window).scrollTop(scrollPos); 


